# Privacy Policy — Vaktija TV System

**Last updated: April 1, 2026**
**Contact: maricsadzid@gmail.com**

## Overview
Vaktija TV is a two-app system (TV display + Admin app) for displaying 
Islamic prayer times and announcements in mosques.

## Data We Collect

### Admin App
- **Email address** — used for Firebase Authentication login only
- **Images** — uploaded by admins and stored on Cloudinary

### TV App
- **No personal data collected** — the TV app only reads and displays data

## How We Use Data
- Email is used solely for authentication purposes
- Images are used solely for displaying mosque announcements
- No data is sold or shared with third parties

## Data Storage
- Authentication data is stored securely by Google Firebase
- Images are stored securely by Cloudinary
- No data is stored locally except the mosque ID on the TV device

## Third Party Services
- [Google Firebase](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)
- [Cloudinary](https://cloudinary.com/privacy)

